Introduction

Hyunmin is a South Korean rapper under MYSTIC Story. He is the leader and main rapper of the boy group ARrC.

Hyunmin was first known as one of the contestants on the 2023 survival show Boys Planet under Jellyfish Entertainment. He was officially introduced on December 29, 2022 as Park Hyun Been. He competed in the show until his eventual elimination in the 8th episode, ranking 48th place.

On July 8, 2024, MYSTIC Story announced their first boy group to the public named ARrC. Hyunmin was revealed to be one of the 7 members of this group.
